<b><a name="2.2.1">2.2.1</a> Advanced Power Management</b></p>
<p>
Advanced Power Management is not supported by Windows&nbsp;NT&nbsp;4.0. As a result, you should remove Advanced Power Management features before installing SP6.</p>

