<b><a name="2.2.2">2.2.2</a> Power Management Utilities</b></p>
<p>
Power Management Utilities may not work on Windows&nbsp;NT&nbsp;4.0 SP6. Contact the vendor of your Power Management Utilities for an updated version that is compatible with Windows&nbsp;NT&nbsp;4.0 SP6.</p>

