<p><b><a name="2.2.3">2.2.3</a> 3Com EtherLink 905B NIC Driver</b></p>
There is a known issue with the 3Com EtherLink 905B network adapter driver prior to version 3.38.40.0. If an earlier version of the driver is detected during SP6 installation, it will be replaced with version 3.40.40.0. If you have an EtherLink 905B network adapter and need to reinstall the drivers, you can obtain the latest drivers from 3Com’s Web site at:<br>
<a href="http://www.3com.com">http://www.3com.com</a></p>

